name: 京剧服饰 The clothes of Beijing Opera
description:

一些tag: clothes_jingju,1girl, solo,_____ hair, hair ornament, makeup,portrait,grey background, upper body, long hair,simple background, chinese clothes, _____ eyes, long sleeves, flower,closed mouth

The best resolution is 832x1024，50 steps, low cfg

建议以832x1024，50步及以上低cfg运行该模型

Portrait and upper bust have the best effect

Based on nai model.

Training by the stage photos and fixed makeup photos of Beijing Opera.

以京剧剧照和定妆照为训练集。

The original model is a real person model.I have merged it with one private model，because of the merge ,this model has a unique facial and fabric effect
